# Contact form email delivery (https://resend.com — free tier: 3,000 emails/month)
#
# 1. Sign up at https://resend.com
# 2. Go to API Keys → Create API Key (permission: "Sending access" is enough)
# 3. Paste it below in .env.local, then restart the dev server
#
# Until a real domain is verified in Resend, messages can only be delivered
# to the email address the Resend account was created with — so sign up
# with the same address as `site.email` in src/lib/site.ts.
RESEND_API_KEY=
